## Venter (Human footprint) layers:
http://datadryad.org/resource/doi:10.5061/dryad.052q5.2
Venter O, Sanderson EW, Magrach A, Allan JR, Beher J, Jones KR, Possingham HP, Laurance WF, Wood P, Fekete BM, Levy MA, Watson JE (2016) Global terrestrial Human Footprint maps for 1993 and 2009. Scientific Data 3: 160067. http://dx.doi.org/10.1038/sdata.2016.67

Venter O, Sanderson EW, Magrach A, Allan JR, Beher J, Jones KR, Possingham HP, Laurance WF, Wood P, Fekete BM, Levy MA, Watson JEM (2016) Data from: Global terrestrial Human Footprint maps for 1993 and 2009. Dryad Digital Repository. http://dx.doi.org/10.5061/dryad.052q5.2

Datadryad requests citing both the paper and the repository.

## National land cover database
https://www.mrlc.gov/nlcd11_data.php

Preferred NLCD 2011 citation: Homer, C.G., Dewitz, J.A., Yang, L., Jin, S., Danielson, P., Xian, G., Coulston, J., Herold, N.D., Wickham, J.D., and Megown, K., 2015, Completion of the 2011 National Land Cover Database for the conterminous United States-Representing a decade of land cover change information. Photogrammetric Engineering and Remote Sensing, v. 81, no. 5, p. 345-354

## Active mines
https://mrdata.usgs.gov/mineral-resources/active-mines.html

"Mine plants and operations for commodities monitored by the National Minerals Information Center of the USGS. Operations included are those considered active in 2003 and surveyed by the USGS."

https://mrdata.usgs.gov/mineplant/
Active Mines and Mineral Processing Plants in the United States in 2003
https://mrdata.usgs.gov/metadata/mineplant.txt
Citation_Information:
        Originator: U.S. Geological Survey
        Publication_Date: 2005
        Title: Active Mines and Mineral Processing Plants in the United States in 2003
        Geospatial_Data_Presentation_Form: vector digital data
        Publication_Information:
          Publication_Place: Reston, Virginia
          Publisher: U.S. Geological Survey
        Online_Linkage: https://mrdata.usgs.gov/mineplant/


## MRDS
